	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000931_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">15<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> Dec<hi rend="sup">r</hi> 1856</p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Mission House</placeName></p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Friend</p>
<lb/><p>Your very 
<lb/>welcome note of the 
<lb/>3<hi rend="sup">d</hi> I found on my arrival 
<lb/>on Wednesday night &amp; 
<lb/>now thank you for 
<lb/>its contents. We came 
<lb/>from Southampton 
<lb/>on Saturday whither 
<lb/>I had gone to bring 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi> L.</persName> We have several 
<lb/>meetings to attend and 
<lb/>will as soon as possible 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000931_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>go to visit my poor 
<lb/><persName>mother</persName> in Scotland<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I shall have very little 
<lb/>time to spend in England 
<lb/>as 110 men wait for 
<lb/>me at <placeName>Tete</placeName> and I must 
<lb/>get through the <placeName>Quilimane 
<lb/>Delta</placeName> before the unhealthy 
<lb/>season begins. You 
<lb/>have heard of the loss 
<lb/>of <persName>my father</persName> than 
<lb/>whom there is none 
<lb/>in England I should 
<lb/>have liked better to have 
<lb/>narrated my adventures<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000931_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/>I have <choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> no letter 
<lb/>since one in 1852 from 
<lb/><persName>Mary</persName> when <persName>Mamma</persName>
<lb/>whom we all dearly 
<lb/>loved and whose 
<lb/>memory we revere 
<lb/>was not expected to 
<lb/>live. We have no 
<lb/>idea how we shall 
<lb/>be situated but it will 
<lb/>be in some quiet spot 
<lb/>near London proper 
<lb/>for writing. I shall 
<lb/>not engage in 
<lb/>speechifying. Present 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000931_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/>our kindest regards to 
<lb/>all your family &amp; 
<lb/>believe me ever 
<lb/>Affectionately Yours 
<lb/>David Livingston</p>
			
</div>
